ur Monkey Mind &#x26; Calm Your Thinking</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Achieving goals: the importance of the Weekly Review","date":"July 27, 2022","description":"The Weekly Review has the power of getting you to zoom out from the day to day grind of completing tasks, to look at the big picture and make sure that you know why you are doing what you are doing and how that aligns to your goals and values."}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/make-alias-imports-work-gatsby-typescript/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Make alias imports work in Gatsby with TypeScript"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/tips-to-read-more/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"8 tips to read more books"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"ece373e1-f5ff-5bab-a6aa-4c2c901a9889","previousPostId":"4fb30a4e-8e31-516a-aeeb-04549aeb4bf2","nextPostId":"62e29e97-b8d6-5b0c-a36e-cfd85f3ef73a"}},
